Test Cases for Missile Game 

Shooting the missile (right click happy path) 
Precondition: Player runs the solution (starts the game) 
Action: User clicks the right mouse button  
Postcondition: Missile is launched  

Shooting the missile (space bar happy path) 
Precondition: Player runs the solution (starts the game) 
Action: User clicks the spacebar  
Postcondition: Missile is launched 

Shooting the missile (right click unhappy path) 
Precondition: Player runs the solution (starts the game) 
Action: User clicks the right mouse button  
Postcondition: Error, missile is not launched  

Shooting the missile (spacebar unhappy path) 
Precondition: Player runs the solution (starts the game) 
Action: User clicks the spacebar  
Postcondition: Error, missile is not launched  


Missile colliding with ship (happy path) 
Precondition: Missile successfully launches 
Action: Missile hits a ship   
Postcondition: Ship blows up, missile and ship removed from screen 

Missile colliding with ship (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Missile successfully launches 
Action: Missile hits a ship   
Postcondition: Error, solution does not display an explosion 

Missile colliding with ship (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Missile successfully launches 
Action: Missile hits a ship   
Postcondition: Error, solution does not remove missile and ship from screen 

Missile colliding with ship (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Missile successfully launches 
Action: Missile appears to collide with a ship   
Postcondition: Error, solution does not detect the ship, missile goes through it 

Missile colliding with ship (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Missile successfully launches 
Action: Missile hits a ship   
Postcondition: Error, solution does not remove ship from screen but removes missile, or vice versa 


End game (happy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User is idle for 5 minutes   
Postcondition: Solution ends the game   

End game (happy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User clicks left mouse button   
Postcondition: Solution ends the game   

End game (happy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User presses esc button   
Postcondition: Solution ends the game  

End game (happy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: "hit” count reaches 10 
Postcondition: Solution  ends the game 

End game (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User is idle for 5 minutes   
Postcondition: Solution does not end the game 

End game (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User clicks left mouse button 
Postcondition: Solution does not end the game  

End game (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: User presses esc button 
Postcondition: Solution does not end the game 

End game (unhappy path) 
Precondition: Solution is running 
Action: “hit” count reaches 10 
Postcondition: Solution does not end the game 
